The paper focuses on the application of machine learning and deep learning algorithms for IoT data classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also specifically mentions IoT domains, indicating a strong connection to cs.IOT (Internet of Things). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence techniques, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also evaluates the performance of algorithms, which could be related to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.DB (Databases).
